1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 13=

26
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:29,280
You're still the same,

27
00:01:29,590 --> 00:01:30,710
standing out wherever you go.

28
00:01:31,790 --> 00:01:32,630
So do you.

29
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,120
Come on, cheers.

30
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,510
Looking forward to working with you.

31
00:01:35,510 --> 00:01:36,790
Life really is full of surprises.

32
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,510
Zhi'er was always so low-key.

33
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,760
Now, she's Linhai's CEO.

34
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:42,280
With his wife backing him up,

35
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:44,150
Tingyu is much stronger.

36
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:46,310
I guess it won't be long before you two

37
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:48,640
help Luzhou Group grow even more.

38
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:50,760
You're overthinking it.

39
00:01:51,710 --> 00:01:52,710
Luzhou and Linhai

40
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,430
have always been partners.

41
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,099
I wouldn't call it help.

42
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,120
Besides,

43
00:01:58,150 --> 00:02:00,310
Tingyu doesn't seem focused on work.

44
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:04,590
You always get right to the point.

45
00:02:05,310 --> 00:02:06,590
I remember back in college,

46
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,400
you were already a big deal.

47
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:10,400
A lot of girls had a crush on you.

48
00:02:11,910 --> 00:02:13,360
They thought your name sounded

49
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,840
pretty stylish backwards.

50
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,286
Everyone kept wondering

51
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:18,680
if you were Xiao Ting, that rising star

52
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,640
in finance.

53
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,240
It was just a rumor.

54
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:25,750
Do you have a girlfriend now?

55
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,800
No.

56
00:02:35,330 --> 00:02:36,210
Then what about me?

57
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,310
But I already like someone.

58
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,430
What kind of girl is that lucky?

59
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,710
She's an online blogger,

60
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:49,470
gentle and graceful,

61
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,000
smart and brave.

62
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,460
Whenever something happens,

63
00:02:53,746 --> 00:02:55,066
she's always the first to step up.

64
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,400
Anyway,

65
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:59,360
to me, she's truly one of a kind.

66
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,310
You really have great taste.

67
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,280
From what you said,

68
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:13,630
she's an investigative blogger, right?

69
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:16,190
She stands up for what's right

70
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:17,960
and writes with real skill.

71
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,270
That's good.

72
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:23,430
Better than some people
scheming all day.

73
00:03:24,190 --> 00:03:25,030
Zhi'er,

74
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,750
when you twisted your ankle,

75
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:27,910
I was worried sick

76
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:29,310
that you'd get me wrong.

77
00:03:30,710 --> 00:03:32,470
Yuqing, why would I?

78
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:34,550
I get it.

79
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,680
There are clients over there.

80
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,960
I'll go say hello.

81
00:03:58,590 --> 00:04:00,240
The updated Lianxin Island files

82
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,200
are here.

83
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,680
Sis,

84
00:04:03,150 --> 00:04:04,680
do my dark circles look bad?

85
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,579
Will I end up looking worn out

86
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:08,240
at a young age?

87
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,870
Thanks for the hard work, cutie.

88
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,240
After all of this,

89
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:14,800
I'll take you to a spa.

90
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,720
I promise you will be glowing.

91
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:17,790
Okay.

92
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:19,590
I am motivated again.

93
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,160
Am I interrupting?

94
00:04:23,450 --> 00:04:24,330
Bai.

95
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,430
Not at all. Come in.

96
00:04:27,270 --> 00:04:28,120
You and the boss

97
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:29,720
asked me to look into your birth mom.

98
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:30,790
I found a lead.

99
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,840
Her name is Wen Hui.

100
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:35,190
Her household registration record
is active.

101
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:38,830
You mean

102
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:41,270
she's still alive?

103
00:04:43,630 --> 00:04:45,630
But we still don't have her address.

104
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,732
People on Lianxin Island
should know her.

105
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,680
I'll go check again later.

106
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:54,700
(Permanent Resident Registration Card,
Wen Hui)

107
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:59,480
Thanks, Bai.

108
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,720
It's the least I could do.

109
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:03,110
I'm heading out now.

110
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,390
If you need anything, just call me.

111
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:07,150
Thanks.

112
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,830
Lianxin Island.

113
00:05:29,916 --> 00:05:31,089
- Ma'am.
- Once relocated...

114
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,400
Ma'am,

115
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,480
excuse me.

116
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:39,310
Do you know someone named Wen Hui?

117
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,560
Miss,

118
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,750
didn't you ask me that over there?

119
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,440
Thanks.

120
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:55,870
They're twins.

121
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,720
You came for Mom too?

122
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,750
The locals said

123
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:08,720
she only comes back now and then,

124
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:11,750
so they don't know where she lives.

125
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,270
What are they doing?

126
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,750
People here are simple and warm.

127
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,800
They often gather together

128
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,510
to sing and dance.

129
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,840
That's really nice.

130
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,920
I've seen you dance.

131
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,070
You looked great dancing.

132
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,830
When was that?

133
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,000
Last time,

134
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:42,830
when you were with Lu Tingxiao,

135
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,560
I was there too.

136
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,270
But later,

137
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:47,950
Lu Tingyu showed up,

138
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:49,670
and then you left.

139
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,480
So, that's why
he suddenly dragged me away.

140
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:01,240
While seeing you dancing,

141
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,840
I was really jealous.

142
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,800
When I was little,

143
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,120
I loved dancing too.

144
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,680
Dancing? For what?

145
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,120
Just like your mom.

146
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:30,350
Don't dance!

147
00:07:33,430 --> 00:07:34,290
Sir,

148
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,830
my daughter dances pretty well.

149
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:38,040
Why not let her perform for you?

150
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,080
Go on, dance.

151
00:07:45,750 --> 00:07:47,480
Dance, or no meal.

152
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,440
Dance.

153
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:15,640
Later,

154
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:19,040
to secure ties with the Lus,

155
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:22,190
Lin Youqiang gave me away like a gift.

156
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:27,160
I became a hostage,

157
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,150
a decoration,

158
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,000
and a punching bag.

159
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,510
Not a Lin came for me.

160
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,480
So, I hate them.

161
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:39,030
I hated the Lins.

162
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,440
So, I found you.

163
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:44,360
I hoped you'd help me end all this.

164
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,200
It's all over now.

165
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,160
Lin Youqiang

166
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:56,240
lied, cheated,
and left his wife and kids.

167
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,000
He's already paid the price.

168
00:09:01,630 --> 00:09:03,240
I've never told anyone this before.

169
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:06,630
Somehow,

170
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,510
it all came pouring out to you.

171
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,240
Because we're real sisters.

172
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,240
We have the same blood in us.

173
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,280
Come on.

174
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:26,840
There's not a Lin

175
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,200
or a Lu.

176
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,440
There are only simple people

177
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,390
and the welcoming sea.

178
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:35,750
Dance with me.

179
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:37,320
It's okay even if you miss a step.

180
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:05,230
Come on.

181
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:21,440
We're not young anymore.

182
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,120
You're all here.

183
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:25,630
Wen Hui,

184
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,600
some twins were looking for you.

185
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,680
They're over there.

186
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:45,180
(Wen Hui, mother of Wen Yan
and Lin Zhi'er)

187
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:50,750
Let's go.

188
00:11:04,300 --> 00:11:05,780
(Sustainable Development)

189
00:11:06,150 --> 00:11:08,790
(Construction Permit)
(Lianxin Island was meant for tourism,)

190
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:11,510
(but approved for commercial residence.)

191
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:13,650
(How exactly)

192
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:15,120
(was this permit approved?)

193
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,040
Boss,

194
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:25,643
you had me look into the Lins' crash.

195
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:26,630
There is a twist.

196
00:11:27,026 --> 00:11:28,166
The crash wasn't an accident.

197
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,630
Someone tampered with it.

198
00:11:29,870 --> 00:11:31,920
The police
have quietly reopened the case.

199
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:33,510
Got it.

200
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,080
Where did you go?

201
00:11:48,216 --> 00:11:49,276
You didn't answer my calls.

202
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,240
I went to Lianxin Island.

203
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,510
My phone died.

204
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:55,750
The report
on the Lins' car crash is out.

205
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:59,040
It wasn't an accident.

206
00:12:02,860 --> 00:12:05,380
(Traffic Accident Investigation Report)

207
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:09,660
(The brake system shows
clear signs of tampering.)

208
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,000
It was murder.

209
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,320
Who could've done it?

210
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:16,390
An enemy?

211
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:17,630
A business rival?

212
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,510
Could it be Lin Zhi'er?

213
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,080
She hated Lin Youqiang.

214
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,270
Don't jump to conclusions.

215
00:12:33,616 --> 00:12:34,842
The police are looking into it.

216
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,600
We'll have answers soon.

217
00:12:38,510 --> 00:12:39,350
I'm just

218
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,080
a little scared.

219
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:49,470
Don't be scared.

220
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:50,870
I'm here with you.

221
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:27,660
♪This door♪

222
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:32,810
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

223
00:13:33,290 --> 00:13:36,850
♪With a voice even lighter♪

224
00:13:36,850 --> 00:13:39,660
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

225
00:13:40,110 --> 00:13:41,480
♪I know now♪

226
00:13:41,810 --> 00:13:46,690
♪What the chill in my body means♪

227
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:49,910
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

228
00:13:50,110 --> 00:13:53,530
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

229
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:56,690
♪To complete♪

230
00:13:57,150 --> 00:14:00,900
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

231
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:03,540
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

232
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:07,230
♪Like a door with no key♪

233
00:14:07,540 --> 00:14:09,860
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

234
00:14:09,860 --> 00:14:13,440
♪The tears in my eyes♪

235
00:14:14,150 --> 00:14:16,700
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

236
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:18,440
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

237
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:21,280
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

238
00:14:21,490 --> 00:14:23,580
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

239
00:14:23,730 --> 00:14:28,060
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

240
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,730
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

241
00:14:30,730 --> 00:14:35,400
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
